org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation
Class AeMessageExchangeValidationVisitor

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.visitors.AeAbstractDefVisitor
      org.activebpel.rt.bpel.def.validation.AeMessageExchangeValidationVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeDefVisitor
public class AeMessageExchangeValidationVisitor
extends AeAbstractDefVisitor

Visits the receives and replies to ensure that they're matched up with their plink, operation, and message exchange values.
